OL,3,C'Former British soldier' captured by
OL,4,CRussia while fighting in Ukraine
OL,6,FA British man, who says he used to be
OL,7,Fa private in the army, has been
OL,8,Fcaptured by Russian forces while
OL,9,Ffighting for Ukraine.
OL,11,FIn a widely circulated video on
OL,12,FSunday, first posted on Telegram, the
OL,13,Fman identifies himself as James Scott
OL,14,FRhys Anderson, aged 22, and says he is
OL,15,Fa former British Army soldier.
OL,17,FHe is dressed in combat fatigues and
OL,18,Fspeaks with an English accent while
OL,19,Fappearing to have his hands tied.
