OL,3,C'Former British soldier' captured by
OL,4,CRussia while fighting in Ukraine
OL,6,FHe said to the camera: "I was in the
OL,7,FBritish Army before, from 2019 to
OL,8,F2023, 22 Signal Regiment. Just a
OL,9,Fprivate. I was a signalman. One Signal
OL,10,FBrigade, 22 Signal Regiment, 252
OL,11,FSquadron."
OL,13,FHe said he signed up to fight for
OL,14,FUkraine's International Legion after
OL,15,Flosing his job."When I left, I got
OL,16,Ffired from my job, I applied on the
OL,17,FInternational Legion webpage. I had
OL,18,Fjust lost everything. I just lost my
OL,19,Fjob," he said.
